message: Sean Dean admitted he conspired to traffic four minor girls to engage in commercial sex acts for his financial benefit. He used social media and cellphones to recruit, monitor, direct and communicate with the four girls and woman. He also would rent hotel rooms across Maryland and would use a website to advertise the victims for sex acts. #Maryland #sextrafficking https://buff.ly/2Wxnfoc
